text: Icking is a municipality in Bad Tölz-Wolfratshausen, a district (Landkreis) in Upper Bavaria. == Geography == === Townships === It consists of: * Attenhausen * Dorfen * Holzen * Icking * Irschenhausen * Meilenberg * Obere Alpe * Schützenried * Schlederloh * Spatzenloh * Wadlhausen * Walchstadt == References == ==Other websites== Category:Bad Tölz-Wolfratshausen
